data.description: Check out this gorgeous brick front home located in The Lake at Mundy's Mill Subdivision in Jonesboro, Ga. Boasting 5 spacious bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and newly installed luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, this residence is a must see! Upon entry you will find an inviting 2-story foyer with a catwalk overlooking, separate living room and dining room, an open concept kitchen looking out to the family room offering 42" cabinets, granite countertops, complimented by barely used black appliances. Also, on the main level is a generous sized bedroom and full bathroom simply perfect for overnight guests. The upper level offers an oversized owners suite with sitting area and ensuite offering a dual vanity sink, walk in closet, separate tub and shower, and a water closet for your privacy. Large secondary bedrooms offering tons of natural light, the laundry room, and hall bathroom also adorn the second floor. The fenced in backyard is huge and offers a covered patio perfect for relaxing after a long day's work or family cookout! Trust me you do not want to miss out on this one. This immaculately maintained, barely lived in home is perfect for you and your family!     One last feature, the HOA just built a new clubhouse near the serene community lake and pier for your enjoyment.
